3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as tracking algorithms often use machine learning and AI techniques. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as machine learning is often used in tracking algorithms. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as object tracking is used in video indexing and surveillance applications.
